# KeyPilot App Shell & UI Design

## Module List (8 modules, order)

PropertyVault, ShowingHQ, ClientKeep, FarmTrackr, TaskPilot, MarketPilot, SellerPulse, Insight.

## Header Architecture

- **Sidebar width:** 240px
- **Header height:** 64px
- **Left brand area:** 240px, right border, generous padding, KeyPilot logo as platform anchor
- **Middle:** Module nav (workspace tabs), left padding so it doesn't crowd the logo
- **Right:** Global controls (profile, notifications)

## Module Tabs

- Premium workspace-tab feel, not plain links
- Horizontal spacing between items
- Active: semibold, darker color, bottom border or pill highlight
- Subtle transition on hover

## Sidebar

- 240px width, contextual to selected module
- Grouped sections with labels (e.g. OVERVIEW, SHOWINGS, VISITORS, SYSTEM)
- Strong active state, better hover, consistent icon sizing
- Premium SaaS left rail feel

## Main Content

- Max width: 1200px–1280px
- Clear page title, subtitle where relevant
- Generous but controlled spacing, consistent card alignment

## Design Language

- Clean, light interface; subtle borders; soft radius; restrained shadows
- Strong spacing discipline; limited accent color; strong typography hierarchy
- No clutter; no generic dashboard-template feel

## FarmTrackr

First-class module. Sidebar: Overview, Farms, Farm Lists, Routes/Areas, Mailing Plans, Campaign History, Contacts in Farms, Performance, Templates, Settings.
